{
  "name": "Create Pact Weapon",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This feature does not currently handle selecting an owned weapon to use as your pact weapon.</p><p>This feature requires the \"Personal Item Compendium\" setting to be set.</p><p>This compendium must have all weapons for this feature inside of it.</p><p>Large compendiums may take a moment to process when first using this feature after loading into the game.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">After casting this spell a new feature called \"Dismiss Pact Weapon\" will be available in your features.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" it will automatically be favorited.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Signika, sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\">If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" it will be in it's own section called \"Pact Weapon.\"</span></p><p><em>This feature is safe to rename.</em></p>",
